  "title": "HR & Admin Executive (2 years contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Work Pass administration for work permit, S pass, Epass  (Application, Renewal and Cancellation and purchasing security bond).</li><li>Updating salary, contacts details and new passport number to MOM (OFWAS).</li><li>Preparation for employment contract </li><li>Personal file creation and update in Synergix system and maintain employee records.</li><li>Monitor and regularly filing of worker’s personnel files.</li><li>PCP registration for new workers</li><li>Personal file creation and update Synergix system and maintain employee records.</li><li>Coordinate to arrange Dormitory arrangement for new worker</li><li>Enrolling workers for mandatory courses such as CSOC , AWSHPP etc.</li><li>Responsible for full Worker payroll processing.</li><li>Timesheet updating in the system.</li><li>Worker’s leave updating in the system</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Degree/ Diploma/ A’ Level/ in HR related field with minimum 2 years of relevant working experience.</li><li>Must be able to communicate in both Chinese and English.</li><li>Prefer short notice or immediate available</li><li>Good interpersonal, meticulous and detail-oriented.</li><li>Comfortable working in fast-paced environment.</li><li>Knowing Synergix ERP software will be an added advantage.</li><li>Able to work independently.</li></ul><p></p>",
